{"_id":"8NNokL69uVSp9Rcc","name":"The Respectable Mr. and Mrs. Mars","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/lost-stories-exclusives-the-respectable-mr-and-mrs-mars.png","items":[{"_id":"uIo5zM9QCWbAkrMD","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Respectable Mr. and Mrs. Mars","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-principal.the-respectable-mr-and-mrs-mars","ownerKey":"cazador.the-respectable-mr-and-mrs-mars","role":"principal-descriptor","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"If you do, you will recover 2 Soma and gain 1 Invasion! Token.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 6.","positive":"If you do, you will recover 2 Soma and gain 1 Invasion! Token.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"The Respectable Mr. and Mrs. Mars","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-principal.the-respectable-mr-and-mrs-mars"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241656,"modifiedTime":1783973241656,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"yEpMRU0bc2vMn39H","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Respectable Mr. and Mrs. Mars","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.the-respectable-mr-and-mrs-mars","ownerKey":"cazador.the-respectable-mr-and-mrs-mars","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1}},"system":{"description":"We are a harmless middle-aged couple and no one would ever consider \nus a danger. We are adept at going unnoticed. Our passion for human \nfood drives us to real binges.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 6.","positive":"We are a harmless middle-aged couple and no one would ever consider us a danger. We are adept at going unnoticed. Our passion for human food drives us to real binges.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"The Respectable Mr. and Mrs. Mars","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.the-respectable-mr-and-mrs-mars"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241656,"modifiedTime":1783973241656,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"ZNh0tphqMAc37MOx","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Respectable Mr. and Mrs. Mars","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.the-respectable-mr-and-mrs-mars","ownerKey":"cazador.the-respectable-mr-and-mrs-mars","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2}},"system":{"description":"We are always connected to the Mars Operations Center, and this \nallows us to have information about history and science. We are \nmorbidly attracted to any form of art because it is totally absent on our \nworld.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 6.","positive":"We are always connected to the Mars Operations Center, and this allows us to have information about history and science. We are morbidly attracted to any form of art because it is totally absent on our world.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"The Respectable Mr. and Mrs. Mars","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.the-respectable-mr-and-mrs-mars"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241656,"modifiedTime":1783973241656,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"68hZlhW21yuQvQzv","name":"Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Respectable Mr. and Mrs. Mars","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-darkego.the-respectable-mr-and-mrs-mars","ownerKey":"cazador.the-respectable-mr-and-mrs-mars","role":"dark-ego-descriptor","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"Our knowledge is far more advanced than human knowledge, and we \nhave incredible technology at our disposal. We always try to help those \nwho are considered outcasts or excluded from society...","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 6.","positive":"Our knowledge is far more advanced than human knowledge, and we have incredible technology at our disposal. We always try to help those who are considered outcasts or excluded from society...","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"The Respectable Mr. and Mrs. Mars","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-darkego.the-respectable-mr-and-mrs-mars"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241656,"modifiedTime":1783973241656,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"GJiMcK8mLQxacOVB","name":"Incognito Agents","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Respectable Mr. and Mrs. Mars","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don1.the-respectable-mr-and-mrs-mars","ownerKey":"cazador.the-respectable-mr-and-mrs-mars","role":"gift","sequence":1}},"system":{"description":"Y ou are considered a single Hunter, sharing Soma and \nWounds, and can act 2 times per Exchange. If you are separated, each of you \nwill receive 2 Penalties to any Checks you make alone. At the end of a Scene, \nyou can wipe others’ memory of your being there.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 6.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"The Respectable Mr. and Mrs. Mars","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","key":"don1.the-respectable-mr-and-mrs-mars"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241656,"modifiedTime":1783973241656,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"KsAGXjrirK6jJFxU","name":"Informants","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Respectable Mr. and Mrs. Mars","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don2.the-respectable-mr-and-mrs-mars","ownerKey":"cazador.the-respectable-mr-and-mrs-mars","role":"gift","sequence":2}},"system":{"description":"Once per Scene, you can ask for insight into an NPC, location, or \nevent that has occurred. The Storyteller will provide you with information useful \nto your objectives. Once per Scene, if you witness the unleashing of technology, \nan invention, or a magical power, you can report back to the Operations Center.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 6.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"The Respectable Mr. and Mrs. Mars","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","key":"don2.the-respectable-mr-and-mrs-mars"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241656,"modifiedTime":1783973241656,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"56xXU4GmoiiwBJgW","name":"Dark Ego - Alien Technology","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Respectable Mr. and Mrs. Mars","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","contentKey":"darkego.the-respectable-mr-and-mrs-mars","ownerKey":"cazador.the-respectable-mr-and-mrs-mars","role":"dark-ego","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"Y ou can always take advantage of your \nspecial Equipment:\n1. Laser Pistol: An accurate and silent firearm capable of ignoring all \ncommon defenses. Wounds inflicted cannot be healed until the end of the \nScenario. When a target is eliminated, it becomes a pile of ashes and cannot be \nhealed, even with special Gifts.\n2. Fog Generator: Instantly creates a thick black smoke that blocks the \nvisibility of non-aliens. The smoke lasts for a few minutes but can be quickly \ndispersed by a strong wind.\n3. Portable Tripod: A small multifunctional vehicle that moves on three legs \nand can carry up to six passengers. The Tripod can reach up to nine feet in \nheight and can easily avoid obstacles thanks to its flexible legs. \nWhenever you use alien technology and one or more NPCs witness it, you \nget 1 Invasion! Token. At the end of each Scene in which you have used the \nDark Ego, the Storyteller rolls 1 die for each Invasion! Token. If they roll at \nleast one 6, the Invasion! Tokens are reset and your comrades initiate an attack \non Earth. The Storyteller introduces 4 Martian Agents into the Scenario, who, \nif not eliminated by the end of it, will force you to return to the Operations \nCenter, removing you from the current Campaign.\nMartian Agent - OL Medium 5 - (1 Wound)\nDescriptor: I am an alien skilled in guerrilla warfare. My monstrous appearance \nparalyzes foolish humans with terror. \nAgenda: Eliminate all humans, starting with the most dangerous individuals: \nthe Hunters of the Order.\nGift - Armed for Invasion: A Martian Agent can use a single effect of Alien \nTechnology 1 time per Scene.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 6.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Show off your alien nature by using strange technology or revealing \nyour true identity.","owner":"The Respectable Mr. and Mrs. Mars","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","key":"darkego.the-respectable-mr-and-mrs-mars"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241656,"modifiedTime":1783973241656,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"ymLcGC1YWfIsEij4","name":"Well-made clothes","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Respectable Mr. and Mrs. Mars","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment1.the-respectable-mr-and-mrs-mars","ownerKey":"cazador.the-respectable-mr-and-mrs-mars","role":"equipment","sequence":1}},"system":{"description":"Well-made clothes","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 6.","quantity":1,"owner":"The Respectable Mr. and Mrs. Mars","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","key":"equipment1.the-respectable-mr-and-mrs-mars"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241656,"modifiedTime":1783973241656,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"HwygytDxjfPKVS5E","name":"Walking umbrella and pipe","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Respectable Mr. and Mrs. Mars","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment2.the-respectable-mr-and-mrs-mars","ownerKey":"cazador.the-respectable-mr-and-mrs-mars","role":"equipment","sequence":2}},"system":{"description":"Walking umbrella and pipe","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 6.","quantity":1,"owner":"The Respectable Mr. and Mrs. Mars","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","key":"equipment2.the-respectable-mr-and-mrs-mars"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241656,"modifiedTime":1783973241656,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"2M7Ns0oYev8NQiu9","name":"A small vase with a strange bright red seedling","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Respectable Mr. and Mrs. Mars","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment3.the-respectable-mr-and-mrs-mars","ownerKey":"cazador.the-respectable-mr-and-mrs-mars","role":"equipment","sequence":3}},"system":{"description":"A small vase with a strange bright red seedling","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 6.","quantity":1,"owner":"The Respectable Mr. and Mrs. Mars","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","key":"equipment3.the-respectable-mr-and-mrs-mars"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241656,"modifiedTime":1783973241656,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"WsbsPNgCtQyRidoi","name":"A box of excellent chocolates","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Respectable Mr. and Mrs. Mars","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment4.the-respectable-mr-and-mrs-mars","ownerKey":"cazador.the-respectable-mr-and-mrs-mars","role":"equipment","sequence":4}},"system":{"description":"A box of excellent chocolates","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 6.","quantity":1,"owner":"The Respectable Mr. and Mrs. Mars","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","key":"equipment4.the-respectable-mr-and-mrs-mars"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241656,"modifiedTime":1783973241656,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"xUR9xUwNOSWwOs0m","name":"Various fake identity documents","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Respectable Mr. and Mrs. Mars","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment5.the-respectable-mr-and-mrs-mars","ownerKey":"cazador.the-respectable-mr-and-mrs-mars","role":"equipment","sequence":5}},"system":{"description":"Various fake identity documents","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 6.","quantity":1,"owner":"The Respectable Mr. and Mrs. Mars","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","key":"equipment5.the-respectable-mr-and-mrs-mars"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241656,"modifiedTime":1783973241656,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"emvYl6k9hVXtBXBi","name":"A portrait of a couple commissioned from a famous painter","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Respectable Mr. and Mrs. Mars","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment6.the-respectable-mr-and-mrs-mars","ownerKey":"cazador.the-respectable-mr-and-mrs-mars","role":"equipment","sequence":6}},"system":{"description":"A portrait of a couple commissioned from a famous painter","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 6.","quantity":1,"owner":"The Respectable Mr. and Mrs. Mars","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","key":"equipment6.the-respectable-mr-and-mrs-mars"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241656,"modifiedTime":1783973241656,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"opuwEp5NBRncn2Da","name":"Source Sheet","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Respectable Mr. and Mrs. Mars","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","contentKey":"source.the-respectable-mr-and-mrs-mars","ownerKey":"cazador.the-respectable-mr-and-mrs-mars","role":"source","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"<p><strong>Lost Stories Exclusives</strong></p><p>Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 6.</p>","notes":"Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 6","owner":"The Respectable Mr. and Mrs. Mars","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","key":"source.the-respectable-mr-and-mrs-mars"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241656,"modifiedTime":1783973241656,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"pregenSlug":"lost-stories-exclusives-the-respectable-mr-and-mrs-mars","pregenCollection":"Lost Stories Exclusives","source":"Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf","pages":"6"}},"system":{"details":{"concept":"Lost Stories Exclusives","origin":"The Respectable Mr. and Mrs. Mars","role":"Hunter of the Order","notes":"If you do, you will recover 2 Soma and gain 1 Invasion! Token."},"resources":{"soma":{"value":5,"max":5},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":3},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":5,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241656,"modifiedTime":1783973241656,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"8U9oLHuDgT49C4GV","name":"Princess Viola of Altomonte","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/lost-stories-exclusives-lost-stories-exclusives-hunter-6.png","items":[{"_id":"e9fKBOsBdDAgYi7w","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Princess Viola of Altomonte","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-principal.princess-viola-of-altomonte","ownerKey":"cazador.princess-viola-of-altomonte","role":"principal-descriptor","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"Porziella, my faithful flea, is always with me and has guarded my \nback like a trusted servant. Over time, I have trained Porziella to \nperform various tasks, including very complex ones. Porziella loves \nhuman blood, and although this disgusts people, I try to satisfy her \nwhenever I can.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 12.","positive":"Porziella, my faithful flea, is always with me and has guarded my back like a trusted servant. Over time, I have trained Porziella to perform various tasks, including very complex ones. Porziella loves human blood, and although this disgusts people, I try to satisfy her whenever I can.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Princess Viola of Altomonte","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-principal.princess-viola-of-altomonte"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241658,"modifiedTime":1783973241658,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"8QmKPaTQvIzuayMY","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Princess Viola of Altomonte","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.princess-viola-of-altomonte","ownerKey":"cazador.princess-viola-of-altomonte","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1}},"system":{"description":"I learned some magic tricks from seven bandits, all of them brothers, \nand I know about arcane arts. I am attracted to magic and want to \ngather all knowledge about it.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 12.","positive":"I learned some magic tricks from seven bandits, all of them brothers, and I know about arcane arts. I am attracted to magic and want to gather all knowledge about it.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Princess Viola of Altomonte","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.princess-viola-of-altomonte"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241658,"modifiedTime":1783973241658,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"v3RLn2DD0Zw72zvU","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Princess Viola of Altomonte","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.princess-viola-of-altomonte","ownerKey":"cazador.princess-viola-of-altomonte","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2}},"system":{"description":"I am courageous and stubborn. When I speak about justice and \nequality, the passion that animates me touches people’s hearts. For me, \nthe cause comes before everything and I am ready to take any action, \neven the most extreme.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 12.","positive":"I am courageous and stubborn. When I speak about justice and equality, the passion that animates me touches people’s hearts. For me, the cause comes before everything and I am ready to take any action, even the most extreme.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Princess Viola of Altomonte","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.princess-viola-of-altomonte"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241658,"modifiedTime":1783973241658,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"nv6NIBZPVIjV7K6I","name":"Porziella the Faithful Flea","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Princess Viola of Altomonte","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don1.princess-viola-of-altomonte","ownerKey":"cazador.princess-viola-of-altomonte","role":"gift","sequence":1}},"system":{"description":"Y our trusty flea follows you like a shadow. \nPorziella is an NPC under your full control with the following profile:\nOL Medium 5 - (3 Wounds)\nDescriptor: I am a flea the size of a dog, my skin is so hard and thick that not \neven a sword can pierce it.\nGift - Loyal Flea: Porziella always recognizes blood by its taste, which allows \nher to follow a trail or recognize who it belongs to without error. Once per \nScenario, Porziella can shield Viola by taking 1 Wound in her place. If she \ndoes this, she will be out of combat until the end of the Scene. If Porziella is \nnot present, Viola can spend 1 Soma to bring her into the Scene immediately, \novercoming all obstacles and impediments.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 12.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Princess Viola of Altomonte","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","key":"don1.princess-viola-of-altomonte"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241658,"modifiedTime":1783973241658,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"98Du55WprRoi8tf2","name":"The Magic of the Seven","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Princess Viola of Altomonte","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don2.princess-viola-of-altomonte","ownerKey":"cazador.princess-viola-of-altomonte","role":"gift","sequence":2}},"system":{"description":"Once per Scenario, you can use any of the \nfollowing powers, but you must have the appropriate Equipment.\n1. Mase’s Earring: It allows you to hear a speech even through a wall.\n2. Nardo’s Soap: Gives you 3 Additional Successes to free yourself from \nropes and chains, or to slip away. \n3. C ola’s Razor: Allows you to inflict 1 Additional Wound with one attack. \n4. Micco’s Staff: Plants sprout to block a passageway; the Storyteller creates a Threat that can absorb up to 3 Wounds before yielding. \n5. Petrullo’s Water: Creates a jet of water that strikes up to 30 feet but does \nno damage. \n6. Ascadeo’s Rock: It can be thrown and will fall exactly where you want it \nto fall, without causing any damage. \n7. Ceccone’s Crossbow: Grants you 2 Additional Successes when you \nshoot a dart.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 12.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Princess Viola of Altomonte","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","key":"don2.princess-viola-of-altomonte"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241658,"modifiedTime":1783973241658,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"UWvbo86UcVemkzus","name":"Dark Ego - Taking Destiny into My Own Hands","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Princess Viola of Altomonte","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","contentKey":"darkego.princess-viola-of-altomonte","ownerKey":"cazador.princess-viola-of-altomonte","role":"dark-ego","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"Nothing and no one \ncan hold you against your will. Y ou are free from all obstacles and can move \nat any time, even in the midst of battle, without anyone being able to block \nor harm you. By spending 1 Soma, you can automatically break down any \nenvironmental obstacle in your way, such as walls, doors, or a tangled web of \nbrambles. Y our presence undermines the authority of the powerful: all NPCs \ntied to any kind of authority lower their OL by 1; all Hunters tied to faith or \nwith strong leadership skills receive 1 Penalty per Check.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 12.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Stand up for someone being oppressed, or openly denounce those \nwho hold power over you.\nEquipment: \nA staff sprouting tendrils / A large bar of soap / A sharp razor / A small \npitcher of water / A perfectly polished rock / A light crossbow / A golden \nearring.\nSoma\n 6\nXP\nWounds \n1.\n2.\n3.\nExtra \nWound.\nI am the Princess of Altomonte, and I succeeded my father by taking full control of his lands. I have always rebelled against the old laws \nof the past, which placed all power in the hands of men. The strength of my ideas was unyielding, leading me to carry out serious acts of \nreprisal against the noble families most tied to the old patriarchal traditions. The Order intervened to stop me, but when they realized that \ntaking me prisoner would make me a martyr, I was offered a deal: join the ranks of the Order to fight the darkness. In exchange, I have \nbeen promised favors and political power with which to change the male-dominated society of my era forever.","owner":"Princess Viola of Altomonte","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","key":"darkego.princess-viola-of-altomonte"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241658,"modifiedTime":1783973241658,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"nzkHSVZyA3huKfAU","name":"Source Sheet","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Princess Viola of Altomonte","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","contentKey":"source.princess-viola-of-altomonte","ownerKey":"cazador.princess-viola-of-altomonte","role":"source","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"<p><strong>Lost Stories Exclusives</strong></p><p>Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 12.</p>","notes":"Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 12","owner":"Princess Viola of Altomonte","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","key":"source.princess-viola-of-altomonte"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241658,"modifiedTime":1783973241658,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"pregenSlug":"lost-stories-exclusives-princess-viola-of-altomonte","pregenCollection":"Lost Stories Exclusives","source":"Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf","pages":"12","contentKey":"hunter.princess-viola-of-altomonte"}},"system":{"details":{"concept":"Lost Stories Exclusives","origin":"Princess Viola of Altomonte","role":"Hunter of the Order","notes":"<p><strong>Lost Stories Exclusives</strong></p><p>Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 12.</p>"},"resources":{"soma":{"value":6,"max":6},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":3},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":5,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241658,"modifiedTime":1783973241658,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"9sYiYE9mAkUH5CBu","name":"Magnifico the Naked Emperor","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/lost-stories-exclusives-lost-stories-exclusives-hunter-9.png","items":[{"_id":"eljCXUoiZFoiBsKc","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Magnifico the Naked Emperor","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-principal.magnifico-the-naked-emperor","ownerKey":"cazador.magnifico-the-naked-emperor","role":"principal-descriptor","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"I have extremely keen eyesight and no detail escapes me. I can see \neverything, even in the dark or in the thickest fog. Sometimes I don’t \nunderstand whether the things I see are real or just a figment of my \nimagination.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 18.","positive":"I have extremely keen eyesight and no detail escapes me. I can see everything, even in the dark or in the thickest fog. Sometimes I don’t understand whether the things I see are real or just a figment of my imagination.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Magnifico the Naked Emperor","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-principal.magnifico-the-naked-emperor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241658,"modifiedTime":1783973241658,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"R3FmES4ApvkGoYry","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Magnifico the Naked Emperor","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.magnifico-the-naked-emperor","ownerKey":"cazador.magnifico-the-naked-emperor","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1}},"system":{"description":"I am used to walking around completely naked, so my physique is \ntough. I hate having unnecessary things on me, except for my beloved \ncrown.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 18.","positive":"I am used to walking around completely naked, so my physique is tough. I hate having unnecessary things on me, except for my beloved crown.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Magnifico the Naked Emperor","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.magnifico-the-naked-emperor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241658,"modifiedTime":1783973241658,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"Y167iSr58Rtrr4UR","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Magnifico the Naked Emperor","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.magnifico-the-naked-emperor","ownerKey":"cazador.magnifico-the-naked-emperor","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2}},"system":{"description":"I am good with words, I know etiquette, and I know how to dazzle the \ncrowd. I cannot refrain from commenting with the utmost sincerity \non the way my interlocutors dress.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 18.","positive":"I am good with words, I know etiquette, and I know how to dazzle the crowd. I cannot refrain from commenting with the utmost sincerity on the way my interlocutors dress.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Magnifico the Naked Emperor","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.magnifico-the-naked-emperor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241659,"modifiedTime":1783973241659,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"gr8mXAexVZ22u7XM","name":"What I Want to See","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Magnifico the Naked Emperor","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don1.magnifico-the-naked-emperor","ownerKey":"cazador.magnifico-the-naked-emperor","role":"gift","sequence":1}},"system":{"description":"If you see it, you can make it real. Y ou can spend 1 \nSoma and say what object you have in front of you. For the rest of the Scene, \nyou can use it as if it were real with all the characteristics it should have. Y ou \nget 1 Additional Success for each Check if you gain a genuine advantage due \nto the fact that others cannot see the object. Y ou can only have one object \ncreated by this Gift at a time. Y ou are completely immune to any effect based \non reducing or nullifying the ability to see.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 18.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Magnifico the Naked Emperor","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","key":"don1.magnifico-the-naked-emperor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241659,"modifiedTime":1783973241659,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"zLG1P7BTyrf8PhPU","name":"What I Don’t Want to See","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Magnifico the Naked Emperor","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don2.magnifico-the-naked-emperor","ownerKey":"cazador.magnifico-the-naked-emperor","role":"gift","sequence":2}},"system":{"description":"Y ou start each Scene in the shadows, and \nas long as you are in this state, no one will notice your presence or the fact \nthat you are completely naked. As long as you do not perform actions that \nmake you the center of attention, you can continue to do whatever you want \nwithout anyone getting in the way, and you will never be singled out for \naction by a possible enemy. Subjects who base their perception on senses \nother than sight can easily detect you. When you perform a conspicuous \naction or decide to draw attention to yourself, you shift into the light. As \nlong as you are in this state, everyone will see you for what you really are. Y ou \nget 1 Additional Success on the first Check you make when you enter this \nstate. Y ou can spend 1 Soma at any time to return to the shadows.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 18.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Magnifico the Naked Emperor","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","key":"don2.magnifico-the-naked-emperor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241659,"modifiedTime":1783973241659,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"vziYOkAVgR3fsD2C","name":"Dark Ego - All Eyes on Me","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Magnifico the Naked Emperor","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","contentKey":"darkego.magnifico-the-naked-emperor","ownerKey":"cazador.magnifico-the-naked-emperor","role":"dark-ego","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"When you choose to be the center of \nattention, you are the king of the party. Decide what you want to wear and \nwhat valuables you want to display, and you will look the part. Y ou will also \nreceive the following benefits:\n1. All NPCs present will be favorably disposed toward you, and you can \ncreate an Agenda for one of them to represent their strong interest in \nyou. Particularly powerful subjects may require a Position Check, at the \nStoryteller’s discretion. \n2. If a lie is told in your presence, the person who told it suffers 1 Wound \ncaused by bleeding from the eyes.\n3. If you help someone permanently improve the aesthetics of a person or \nplace, you gain 1 Soma. \nThe effect of this Gift lasts until the end of the Scene or until you activate \nanother of your Gifts.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 18.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Take a few minutes to prepare for a meeting with someone you \ndeem important. \nEquipment: \nThe precious crown that I always wear on my head. \nSoma\n 5\nXP\nWounds \n1.\n2.\n3.\nExtra \nWound.\nI was a vain ruler and had eyes only for beauty. My heart was pure and my desire to help others was \nsincere, but everyone took advantage of me and clouded my vision with false words. Seeing beyond the wall \nof lies cost me dearly, but now I am not afraid. I see everything as it is, even myself. The Order hired me as a \nHunter, asking only that I use my power in the service of justice, without ulterior motives, without falsehood. \nBut is that really the case? I no longer care, for now, the only truth that matters to me is the one I choose to \ncreate with my mind.","owner":"Magnifico the Naked Emperor","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","key":"darkego.magnifico-the-naked-emperor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241659,"modifiedTime":1783973241659,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"wSJApWxwcFLrO3J8","name":"Source Sheet","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Magnifico the Naked Emperor","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","contentKey":"source.magnifico-the-naked-emperor","ownerKey":"cazador.magnifico-the-naked-emperor","role":"source","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"<p><strong>Lost Stories Exclusives</strong></p><p>Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 18.</p>","notes":"Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 18","owner":"Magnifico the Naked Emperor","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","key":"source.magnifico-the-naked-emperor"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241659,"modifiedTime":1783973241659,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"pregenSlug":"lost-stories-exclusives-magnifico-the-naked-emperor","pregenCollection":"Lost Stories Exclusives","source":"Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf","pages":"18","contentKey":"hunter.magnifico-the-naked-emperor"}},"system":{"details":{"concept":"Lost Stories Exclusives","origin":"Magnifico the Naked Emperor","role":"Hunter of the Order","notes":"<p><strong>Lost Stories Exclusives</strong></p><p>Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 18.</p>"},"resources":{"soma":{"value":5,"max":5},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":3},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":5,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241659,"modifiedTime":1783973241659,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"CF5YTOjHqrnfS4P9","name":"Thumbking the King of Crime","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/lost-stories-exclusives-lost-stories-exclusives-hunter-7.png","items":[{"_id":"7nEOJuhFrYoCpOqo","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Thumbking the King of Crime","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-principal.thumbking-the-king-of-crime","ownerKey":"cazador.thumbking-the-king-of-crime","role":"principal-descriptor","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"Y ou start the Scenario with 6 Pebble Tokens. During a Scene, you can \nspend 1 Pebble to activate one of these effects:\n1. Return to a place you have already visited, this happens very fast \nand allows you to arrive before anyone else, avoiding any possible \nobstacle.\n2. Get information from the Storyteller about a Place’s weaknesses or \ndetails of a procedure, such as an arcane ritual or a guard shift.\n3. Act immediately after another Hunter, but only to perform an action \nthat is not intended to harm anyone. \n4. Pull a useful item from your bag to deal with a Threat that has arisen.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 14.","positive":"Y ou start the Scenario with 6 Pebble Tokens. During a Scene, you can spend 1 Pebble to activate one of these effects: 1. Return to a place you have already visited, this happens very fast and allows you to arrive before anyone else, avoiding any possible obstacle. 2. Get information from the Storyteller about a Place’s weaknesses or details of a procedure, such as an arcane ritual or a guard shift. 3. Act immediately after another Hunter, but only to perform an action that is not intended to harm anyone. 4. Pull a useful item from your bag to deal with a Threat that has arisen.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Thumbking the King of Crime","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-principal.thumbking-the-king-of-crime"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241658,"modifiedTime":1783973241658,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"QJyeNN8IXckpvKzd","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Thumbking the King of Crime","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.thumbking-the-king-of-crime","ownerKey":"cazador.thumbking-the-king-of-crime","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1}},"system":{"description":"I have an unusual mind and remember every detail, even years \nlater. My body is puny and I hate to do strenuous work.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 14.","positive":"I have an unusual mind and remember every detail, even years later. My body is puny and I hate to do strenuous work.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Thumbking the King of Crime","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.thumbking-the-king-of-crime"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241658,"modifiedTime":1783973241658,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"fGBTjDyRw5nCK0Lh","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Thumbking the King of Crime","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.thumbking-the-king-of-crime","ownerKey":"cazador.thumbking-the-king-of-crime","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2}},"system":{"description":"I have charisma to spare and I am a smooth talker who commands \nrespect and admiration. I must always have the last word.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 14.","positive":"I have charisma to spare and I am a smooth talker who commands respect and admiration. I must always have the last word.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Thumbking the King of Crime","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.thumbking-the-king-of-crime"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241658,"modifiedTime":1783973241658,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"nT5e8msZexkZtr7E","name":"Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Thumbking the King of Crime","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-darkego.thumbking-the-king-of-crime","ownerKey":"cazador.thumbking-the-king-of-crime","role":"dark-ego-descriptor","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"It only takes me a few seconds to assess the situation and use it to \nmy advantage. I have a soft spot for loving families who remind me \nof what I will never have.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 14.","positive":"It only takes me a few seconds to assess the situation and use it to my advantage. I have a soft spot for loving families who remind me of what I will never have.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Thumbking the King of Crime","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-darkego.thumbking-the-king-of-crime"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241658,"modifiedTime":1783973241658,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"EbQzIvm6R98HYwQZ","name":"Tiny","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Thumbking the King of Crime","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don1.thumbking-the-king-of-crime","ownerKey":"cazador.thumbking-the-king-of-crime","role":"gift","sequence":1}},"system":{"description":"Y ou know how to go unnoticed, so no one will ever pick you as \na direct target of one of their actions if there is at least one other Hunter \nin the Scene. Y ou can spend 1 Soma to leave a location without anyone \nnoticing, as long as there is at least one other Hunter to attract attention. \nY ou get 1 Additional Success on each Check where you can use your \ndiminutive stature, but you also get 1 Penalty on each Check where you \nhave to use brute force or physical strength.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 14.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Thumbking the King of Crime","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","key":"don1.thumbking-the-king-of-crime"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241658,"modifiedTime":1783973241658,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"MTAOGOyWrwQM3c3d","name":"In the Right Place at the Right Time","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Thumbking the King of Crime","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don2.thumbking-the-king-of-crime","ownerKey":"cazador.thumbking-the-king-of-crime","role":"gift","sequence":2}},"system":{"description":"Y ou don’t get confused easily.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 14.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Thumbking the King of Crime","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","key":"don2.thumbking-the-king-of-crime"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241658,"modifiedTime":1783973241658,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"lDHJJODVXd2K1Ig0","name":"Dark Ego - Infallible Cunning","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Thumbking the King of Crime","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","contentKey":"darkego.thumbking-the-king-of-crime","ownerKey":"cazador.thumbking-the-king-of-crime","role":"dark-ego","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"When you activate this Gift, the \nStoryteller will reveal to you the Downside of all NPCs in the Scene. \nY ou’ll also learn the easiest way to escape from your location and the most \nvaluable item present. When a Hunter (including you) performs a Check \nand gets a Standard Outcome, you can spend 1 Soma to add 1 Increment \nof your choice, including a special effect of a Gift possessed by the Hunter \nperforming the action.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 14.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Take a few minutes to observe the situation and tell the NPC in \nfront of you what you really think of them. \nEquipment: \nA bag of white pebbles / Seven small gold crowns / Valuable coins and \njewels / A mask with the features of an ogre / A pair of valuable traveling \nboots with two hidden stilettos / Contracts and records of secret negotiations \n/ The key to one of your many secret hideouts / A sling. \nSoma\n 6\nXP\nWounds \n1.\n2.\n3.\nExtra \nWound.\nI am the most important criminal of my time, and there are more than a thousand scoundrels in my employ. I have \nsingle-handedly built up my power through cunning, even committing acts that many people consider despicable. \nThose who lecture me on my misdeeds do not understand that the only thing I wanted in my life was a family that loved \nme. The Order disrupted my criminal empire, but when they realized that eliminating me would start a war among \noutlaws across Europe, I was pardoned and welcomed as a Hunter. My gifts and knowledge ensure a constant flow \nof information, which I use to track down whatever the Order is hunting. Locked away in the fortress of my solitude, I \ncontinue to run my empire. Perhaps I can find a true family in the ranks of the Hunters.","owner":"Thumbking the King of Crime","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","key":"darkego.thumbking-the-king-of-crime"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241658,"modifiedTime":1783973241658,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"koQswZYMAKV4gfcO","name":"Source Sheet","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Thumbking the King of Crime","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","contentKey":"source.thumbking-the-king-of-crime","ownerKey":"cazador.thumbking-the-king-of-crime","role":"source","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"<p><strong>Lost Stories Exclusives</strong></p><p>Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 14.</p>","notes":"Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 14","owner":"Thumbking the King of Crime","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","key":"source.thumbking-the-king-of-crime"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241658,"modifiedTime":1783973241658,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"pregenSlug":"lost-stories-exclusives-thumbking-the-king-of-crime","pregenCollection":"Lost Stories Exclusives","source":"Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf","pages":"14","contentKey":"hunter.thumbking-the-king-of-crime"}},"system":{"details":{"concept":"Lost Stories Exclusives","origin":"Thumbking the King of Crime","role":"Hunter of the Order","notes":"Y ou start the Scenario with 6 Pebble Tokens. During a Scene, you can \nspend 1 Pebble to activate one of these effects:\n1. Return to a place you have already visited, this happens very fast \nand allows you to arrive before anyone else, avoiding any possible \nobstacle.\n2. Get information from the Storyteller about a Place’s weaknesses or \ndetails of a procedure, such as an arcane ritual or a guard shift.\n3. Act immediately after another Hunter, but only to perform an action \nthat is not intended to harm anyone. \n4. Pull a useful item from your bag to deal with a Threat that has arisen."},"resources":{"soma":{"value":6,"max":6},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":3},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":5,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241658,"modifiedTime":1783973241658,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"GCwmgaZ2Bf97OmOx","name":"Nema the Beastslayer","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/lost-stories-exclusives-lost-stories-exclusives-hunter-8.png","items":[{"_id":"umPH1whSPprXc0Qk","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Nema the Beastslayer","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-principal.nema-the-beastslayer","ownerKey":"cazador.nema-the-beastslayer","role":"principal-descriptor","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"I am a skilled Hunter and know what it takes to survive in wild \nplaces. I find it hard to trust anyone, but when I do, I never question \nthe good faith of the person I have chosen.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 16.","positive":"I am a skilled Hunter and know what it takes to survive in wild places. I find it hard to trust anyone, but when I do, I never question the good faith of the person I have chosen.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Nema the Beastslayer","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-principal.nema-the-beastslayer"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241658,"modifiedTime":1783973241658,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"asTzwawxk26wqRYD","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Nema the Beastslayer","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.nema-the-beastslayer","ownerKey":"cazador.nema-the-beastslayer","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1}},"system":{"description":"My senses are keen and my body is hardened by the outdoors. I hate \nbig cities, hustle and bustle, and generally can’t stand people who talk \ntoo much.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 16.","positive":"My senses are keen and my body is hardened by the outdoors. I hate big cities, hustle and bustle, and generally can’t stand people who talk too much.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Nema the Beastslayer","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.nema-the-beastslayer"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241658,"modifiedTime":1783973241658,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"2GRF4ZvCOgULSxSB","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Nema the Beastslayer","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.nema-the-beastslayer","ownerKey":"cazador.nema-the-beastslayer","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2}},"system":{"description":"I am trained to kill all kinds of beasts and know how to use the \nhunting grounds to my advantage. Monsters must always be \ndestroyed, for them I see no mercy or redemption.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 16.","positive":"I am trained to kill all kinds of beasts and know how to use the hunting grounds to my advantage. Monsters must always be destroyed, for them I see no mercy or redemption.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Nema the Beastslayer","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.nema-the-beastslayer"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241658,"modifiedTime":1783973241658,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"tjV8UKWxQfkURkA0","name":"Hunting Companion","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Nema the Beastslayer","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don1.nema-the-beastslayer","ownerKey":"cazador.nema-the-beastslayer","role":"gift","sequence":1}},"system":{"description":"Y ou don’t open your heart easily, but occasionally \nyou find companions you can trust. At the beginning of the Scenario, you \nchoose another Hunter as your hunting companion, who will receive 1 \nAdditional Success on all Defense Checks they make while you are in close \nproximity to cover their back. Y ou will always know where your hunting \ncompanion is and can spend 1 Soma to get to where they are, ignoring all \nobstacles. Y ou never speak and cannot express yourself verbally, but your \ncompanion will always clearly understand anything you try to tell them.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 16.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Nema the Beastslayer","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","key":"don1.nema-the-beastslayer"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241658,"modifiedTime":1783973241658,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"S5IV1MCMSr2ZRjuV","name":"Stalking","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Nema the Beastslayer","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don2.nema-the-beastslayer","ownerKey":"cazador.nema-the-beastslayer","role":"gift","sequence":2}},"system":{"description":"No prey can escape you, once per Scene you can find distinct \ntraces in a place or on an object. The Storyteller will reveal a useful piece of \ninformation of your choice: who left the clue, where it is, or a weakness in the \nobject. Y ou can spend 1 Soma to blend into your surroundings: as long as you \ndo not take any conspicuous actions (at the Storyteller’s discretion), Minor \nNPCs will not be able to see you, and you will get 3 Additional Successes on \nany Checks you make to go unnoticed or catch someone off guard.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 16.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Nema the Beastslayer","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","key":"don2.nema-the-beastslayer"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241658,"modifiedTime":1783973241658,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"pBRa4QpyyF0InkPM","name":"Dark Ego - It’s Time to Kill the Beast","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Nema the Beastslayer","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","contentKey":"darkego.nema-the-beastslayer","ownerKey":"cazador.nema-the-beastslayer","role":"dark-ego","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"Once per Scene, if you make an \nattack against an enemy with monstrous characteristics, you automatically \nhit without a Check and your attack inflicts 2 Wounds. All of the Wounds \nyou inflict leave clearly visible marks and cannot be healed by the victim \nuntil the end of the Scenario. When you activate this Gift, the Storyteller will \nreveal to you one Gift of each monstrous opponent in the Scene. \nNote: A “monstrous trait” is defined as any Hunter or NPC with Gifts or \nDescriptors that represent superhuman physical traits and abilities that also \ngive them a monstrous appearance. However, the Storyteller has the final say \non whether or not a Character is monstrous.","notes":"See Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 16.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Openly challenge a monstrous creature by revealing your true nature.\nEquipment: \nThe right weapon for each beast / A cloak that changes color according to \nits surroundings / A small leaf-shaped ocarina / Animal traps / A deer heart \npreserved under spirits / A necklace of wolf fangs. \nSoma\n 6\nXP\nWounds \n1.\n2.\n3.\nExtra \nWound.\nI am a lone beast slayer who has dedicated his entire life to eradicating monsters and aberrations. The \nOne Who Plots in the Shadows corrupted my soul by drawing on the pain of the monsters’ poor victims I \ncould not save. The Order has freed me from this evil influence and welcomed me into its ranks as a strong \narm against all manner of monsters. I do not like to talk or waste time with complicated plans: when it is \ntime to begin the hunt, having my weapons ready is all that matters.","owner":"Nema the Beastslayer","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","key":"darkego.nema-the-beastslayer"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241658,"modifiedTime":1783973241658,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"eGieUgjSCQphOxi8","name":"Source Sheet","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Nema the Beastslayer","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","contentKey":"source.nema-the-beastslayer","ownerKey":"cazador.nema-the-beastslayer","role":"source","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"<p><strong>Lost Stories Exclusives</strong></p><p>Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 16.</p>","notes":"Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 16","owner":"Nema the Beastslayer","source":"Lost Stories Exclusives","category":"hunter","key":"source.nema-the-beastslayer"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241658,"modifiedTime":1783973241658,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"pregenSlug":"lost-stories-exclusives-nema-the-beastslayer","pregenCollection":"Lost Stories Exclusives","source":"Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf","pages":"16","contentKey":"hunter.nema-the-beastslayer"}},"system":{"details":{"concept":"Lost Stories Exclusives","origin":"Nema the Beastslayer","role":"Hunter of the Order","notes":"<p><strong>Lost Stories Exclusives</strong></p><p>Broken Tales - Lost Stories - Exclusive Pre-Gen Hunters.pdf, pages 16.</p>"},"resources":{"soma":{"value":6,"max":6},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":3},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":5,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241658,"modifiedTime":1783973241658,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"IQr4MjdbDfExWJWs","name":"Prince Trollo the Innocent","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/lost-stories-prince-trollo-the-innocent.png","items":[{"_id":"dY80l1s95VQAIAcj","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Prince Trollo the Innocent","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-principal.prince-trollo-the-innocent","ownerKey":"cazador.prince-trollo-the-innocent","role":"principal-descriptor","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"Y ou gain 1 Additional Success for each Check you make when trying \nto persuade someone to do the right thing. Once per Scenario, if you \nsuffer 1 Wound to stand up for what you believe in, you set an example \nfor those who help you. Each ally recovers 1 Soma, and a target of your \nchoice (Hunter or NPC) immediately gains an additional action they \nmust use to try to help you or get you to safety.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 6.","positive":"Y ou gain 1 Additional Success for each Check you make when trying to persuade someone to do the right thing. Once per Scenario, if you suffer 1 Wound to stand up for what you believe in, you set an example for those who help you. Each ally recovers 1 Soma, and a target of your choice (Hunter or NPC) immediately gains an additional action they must use to try to help you or get you to safety.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Prince Trollo the Innocent","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-principal.prince-trollo-the-innocent"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241652,"modifiedTime":1783973241652,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"UB2KBfUOVydJBszp","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Prince Trollo the Innocent","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.prince-trollo-the-innocent","ownerKey":"cazador.prince-trollo-the-innocent","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1}},"system":{"description":"I am a young prince, well-versed in the etiquette of the court. I \nam a diligent student, my favorite subjects being history and \npoetry. I am not ashamed of my strange appearance and I hate to \nhide from others.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 6.","positive":"I am a young prince, well-versed in the etiquette of the court. I am a diligent student, my favorite subjects being history and poetry. I am not ashamed of my strange appearance and I hate to hide from others.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Prince Trollo the Innocent","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.prince-trollo-the-innocent"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241652,"modifiedTime":1783973241652,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"lqCGS9eVYqExX3rP","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Prince Trollo the Innocent","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.prince-trollo-the-innocent","ownerKey":"cazador.prince-trollo-the-innocent","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2}},"system":{"description":"I use these qualities to uphold the good name of my family. I will \nnot allow anyone to violate the ideals of justice and courage with \nwhich I was raised.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 6.","positive":"I use these qualities to uphold the good name of my family. I will not allow anyone to violate the ideals of justice and courage with which I was raised.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Prince Trollo the Innocent","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.prince-trollo-the-innocent"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241652,"modifiedTime":1783973241652,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"vERhvFJOJPMZElHR","name":"Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Prince Trollo the Innocent","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-darkego.prince-trollo-the-innocent","ownerKey":"cazador.prince-trollo-the-innocent","role":"dark-ego-descriptor","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"I have strange powers, and my body is stronger and more resilient \nthan an ordinary child’s. While I’m not ashamed of my \nappearance, these uncanny abilities mark me as different, and I \ntry not to attract attention when I use my power.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 6.","positive":"I have strange powers, and my body is stronger and more resilient than an ordinary child’s. While I’m not ashamed of my appearance, these uncanny abilities mark me as different, and I try not to attract attention when I use my power.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Prince Trollo the Innocent","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-darkego.prince-trollo-the-innocent"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241652,"modifiedTime":1783973241652,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"EB687YBUG5Tie0jk","name":"Noble Birth","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Prince Trollo the Innocent","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don1.prince-trollo-the-innocent","ownerKey":"cazador.prince-trollo-the-innocent","role":"gift","sequence":1}},"system":{"description":"Once per Scene, if you are in a place where your family’s \nauthority is recognized, you can gain access to a restricted location, such \nas a dungeon or castle, or a direct audience with an authority figure. \nAs a prince, you have learned everything a future ruler needs to know. \nOnce per Scene, you gain 2 Additional Successes for an action in which \nyou can demonstrate your knowledge of history and poetry, or your skill \nwith the sword. \nI learned kindness from my mother and firmness from my father.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 6.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Prince Trollo the Innocent","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","key":"don1.prince-trollo-the-innocent"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241652,"modifiedTime":1783973241652,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"Vhp3NZWzWuZvwskH","name":"Good Heart","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Prince Trollo the Innocent","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don2.prince-trollo-the-innocent","ownerKey":"cazador.prince-trollo-the-innocent","role":"gift","sequence":2}},"system":{"description":"Y ou have the innocence and strength of a true ruler.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 6.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Prince Trollo the Innocent","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","key":"don2.prince-trollo-the-innocent"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241652,"modifiedTime":1783973241652,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"Si3HofAoyFRqcHro","name":"Dark Ego - Oknytt’s Legacy","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Prince Trollo the Innocent","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","contentKey":"darkego.prince-trollo-the-innocent","ownerKey":"cazador.prince-trollo-the-innocent","role":"dark-ego","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"Y ou appeal to your Dark Ego to gain \ngreat powers. If it is day, you must spend 1 Soma. If you have no Soma, \nyou take 1 Wound. If it is night, there is no cost to activate this Gift, as \nyou are a creature of the night. Y ou gain the following powers:\n1. Yellow Eyes: See perfectly in total darkness. Once per Scene, you can \nsee a target for what they really are, unmasking any disguise they may \nbe wearing. \n2. Troll Strength: Once per Scene, you can perform an act of unprecedented strength by lifting or moving a weight equal to ten men. If you \nuse your strength to harm someone, you inflict 1 Additional Wound. \n3. Stone Skin: Once per Scene, you can suffer an attack or hazard while \navoiding any Wounds. Y ou can resist almost everything, including fire, \nfalls, and weapons. Only magic can harm you. Y ou must declare the use \nof this effect before any Defense Check.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 6.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"You tap into your heritage in front of someone you have helped \nbefore and who is unaware of your true nature.","owner":"Prince Trollo the Innocent","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","key":"darkego.prince-trollo-the-innocent"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241652,"modifiedTime":1783973241652,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"ioVLZx9VtweDeRNP","name":"Clothes of fine workmanship","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Prince Trollo the Innocent","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment1.prince-trollo-the-innocent","ownerKey":"cazador.prince-trollo-the-innocent","role":"equipment","sequence":1}},"system":{"description":"Clothes of fine workmanship","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 6.","quantity":1,"owner":"Prince Trollo the Innocent","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","key":"equipment1.prince-trollo-the-innocent"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241652,"modifiedTime":1783973241652,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"Y7TWuzz1WBezbn6q","name":"A small wooden crown painted with gold, given to me by my father","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Prince Trollo the Innocent","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment2.prince-trollo-the-innocent","ownerKey":"cazador.prince-trollo-the-innocent","role":"equipment","sequence":2}},"system":{"description":"A small wooden crown painted with gold, given to me by my father","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-s