{"_id":"ZBBwHH25anyLNABr","name":"Tremoteus Rumpel","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/lost-stories-tremoteus-rumpel.png","items":[{"_id":"1XWLJUO1whsXm33S","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Tremoteus Rumpel","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-principal.tremoteus-rumpel","ownerKey":"cazador.tremoteus-rumpel","role":"principal-descriptor","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"I have an encyclopedic memory and there is no law that I don’t \nknow. I hate to break the rules.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 4.","positive":"I have an encyclopedic memory and there is no law that I don’t know. I hate to break the rules.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Tremoteus Rumpel","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-principal.tremoteus-rumpel"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241651,"modifiedTime":1783973241651,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"SAumJIKQDwj8zTcX","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Tremoteus Rumpel","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.tremoteus-rumpel","ownerKey":"cazador.tremoteus-rumpel","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1}},"system":{"description":"My reputation precedes me, and my word is held in the highest \nregard by anyone with an ounce of honesty. I detest criminals and \nthose who act to harm the innocent. Big or small, a crime is still \na crime.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 4.","positive":"My reputation precedes me, and my word is held in the highest regard by anyone with an ounce of honesty. I detest criminals and those who act to harm the innocent. Big or small, a crime is still a crime.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Tremoteus Rumpel","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.tremoteus-rumpel"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241651,"modifiedTime":1783973241651,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"Yabjvt5PSw2HQBdJ","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Tremoteus Rumpel","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.tremoteus-rumpel","ownerKey":"cazador.tremoteus-rumpel","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2}},"system":{"description":"I am a keen disputant and have an uncanny ability to detect \ndeception. I need hard evidence before I’ll accuse someone of \ndishonesty.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 4.","positive":"I am a keen disputant and have an uncanny ability to detect deception. I need hard evidence before I’ll accuse someone of dishonesty.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Tremoteus Rumpel","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.tremoteus-rumpel"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241651,"modifiedTime":1783973241651,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"amWtPe4E69ZnTn4z","name":"Examine the Evidence","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Tremoteus Rumpel","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don1.tremoteus-rumpel","ownerKey":"cazador.tremoteus-rumpel","role":"gift","sequence":1}},"system":{"description":"Y ou can use each of the following effects \nonce per Scene: \n1. For the Record: Y ou can make a note of something a subject has said; \nyou will never forget it. Write it down because you can use it when you \nactivate your Dark Ego. By spending 1 Soma, the Storyteller will reveal a \nweakness of the subject whose words you have memorized.\n2. Consult the Laws: The Storyteller will reveal to you the customs and \nrules of a social group or place you are in. By spending 1 Soma, you \ncan create a loophole, known only to you, to the rules that have been \nrevealed.\n3. The Decisive Proof: When you examine an object, the Storyteller \nwill reveal a quality or feature that few people may notice. By spending \n1 Soma, you will learn who was the last person to own or use what you \nare examining.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 4.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Tremoteus Rumpel","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","key":"don1.tremoteus-rumpel"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241651,"modifiedTime":1783973241651,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"EbcJ69jV7tLgWIwA","name":"Your Honor","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Tremoteus Rumpel","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don2.tremoteus-rumpel","ownerKey":"cazador.tremoteus-rumpel","role":"gift","sequence":2}},"system":{"description":"If you stand in front of nobles, lawmen, or leaders in \ngeneral, you can spend 1 Soma to have them recognize your name or \nreputation. If you use your identity as a strength, you gain 1 Additional \nSuccess. If you give your word in a negotiation, you gain 1 Additional \nSuccess in a possible Position Check.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 4.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Tremoteus Rumpel","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","key":"don2.tremoteus-rumpel"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241652,"modifiedTime":1783973241652,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"rkYkGy50uqAWHBtU","name":"Dark Ego - Shattered Pact","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Tremoteus Rumpel","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","contentKey":"darkego.tremoteus-rumpel","ownerKey":"cazador.tremoteus-rumpel","role":"dark-ego","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"Those who break the rules must be \npunished. Y ou gain 1 Additional Success on all Position and Defense \nChecks you make against a subject who’s acting in a way that contradicts \nthe statement you recorded using the For the Record effect. If you act \nto harm them, you also inflict 1 Additional Wound. Once per Scene, if \na subject reveals themselves as they really are, as opposed to how they \npreviously presented themselves, or if they break their word, you can \nlecture them on their dishonesty. All your companions gain 1 Additional \nSuccess on their next action.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 4.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Make an argument against the guilty by pointing out their \nmisdeeds.","owner":"Tremoteus Rumpel","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","key":"darkego.tremoteus-rumpel"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241652,"modifiedTime":1783973241652,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"SToA5y65uyNxz2Ul","name":"A long lawyer’s robe","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Tremoteus Rumpel","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment1.tremoteus-rumpel","ownerKey":"cazador.tremoteus-rumpel","role":"equipment","sequence":1}},"system":{"description":"A long lawyer’s robe","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 4.","quantity":1,"owner":"Tremoteus Rumpel","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","key":"equipment1.tremoteus-rumpel"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241652,"modifiedTime":1783973241652,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"1S6ozQh0S1yrznXx","name":"A magnifying glass","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Tremoteus Rumpel","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment2.tremoteus-rumpel","ownerKey":"cazador.tremoteus-rumpel","role":"equipment","sequence":2}},"system":{"description":"A magnifying glass","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 4.","quantity":1,"owner":"Tremoteus Rumpel","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","key":"equipment2.tremoteus-rumpel"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241652,"modifiedTime":1783973241652,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"jO4wLWueoEH6KbeL","name":"Documents and deeds from over a hundred trials","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Tremoteus Rumpel","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment3.tremoteus-rumpel","ownerKey":"cazador.tremoteus-rumpel","role":"equipment","sequence":3}},"system":{"description":"Documents and deeds from over a hundred trials","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 4.","quantity":1,"owner":"Tremoteus Rumpel","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","key":"equipment3.tremoteus-rumpel"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241652,"modifiedTime":1783973241652,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"X4sDMGP1WBEJsxXG","name":"A fine dueling sword","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Tremoteus Rumpel","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment4.tremoteus-rumpel","ownerKey":"cazador.tremoteus-rumpel","role":"equipment","sequence":4}},"system":{"description":"A fine dueling sword","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 4.","quantity":1,"owner":"Tremoteus Rumpel","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","key":"equipment4.tremoteus-rumpel"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241652,"modifiedTime":1783973241652,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"hJ0zzp2uUGqVH8op","name":"Property deeds and bank deposits","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Tremoteus Rumpel","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment5.tremoteus-rumpel","ownerKey":"cazador.tremoteus-rumpel","role":"equipment","sequence":5}},"system":{"description":"Property deeds and bank deposits","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 4.","quantity":1,"owner":"Tremoteus Rumpel","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","key":"equipment5.tremoteus-rumpel"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241652,"modifiedTime":1783973241652,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"fsNMOrJIBZ1IQCCS","name":"A ring of little value given to me by my first client","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Tremoteus Rumpel","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment6.tremoteus-rumpel","ownerKey":"cazador.tremoteus-rumpel","role":"equipment","sequence":6}},"system":{"description":"A ring of little value given to me by my first client","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 4.","quantity":1,"owner":"Tremoteus Rumpel","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","key":"equipment6.tremoteus-rumpel"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241652,"modifiedTime":1783973241652,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"AfTeGhMnm57B6ucI","name":"A scroll of recommendations written by the Pope himself","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Tremoteus Rumpel","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment7.tremoteus-rumpel","ownerKey":"cazador.tremoteus-rumpel","role":"equipment","sequence":7}},"system":{"description":"A scroll of recommendations written by the Pope himself","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 4.","quantity":1,"owner":"Tremoteus Rumpel","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","key":"equipment7.tremoteus-rumpel"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241652,"modifiedTime":1783973241652,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"ILjYQUQGAx7kKy71","name":"Source Sheet","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Tremoteus Rumpel","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","contentKey":"source.tremoteus-rumpel","ownerKey":"cazador.tremoteus-rumpel","role":"source","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"<p><strong>Lost Stories</strong></p><p>bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 4.</p>","notes":"bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 4","owner":"Tremoteus Rumpel","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","key":"source.tremoteus-rumpel"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241652,"modifiedTime":1783973241652,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}],"effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"pregenSlug":"lost-stories-tremoteus-rumpel","pregenCollection":"Lost Stories","source":"bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf","pages":"4"}},"system":{"details":{"concept":"Lost Stories","origin":"Tremoteus Rumpel","role":"Hunter of the Order","notes":"<p><strong>Lost Stories</strong></p><p>bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 4.</p>"},"resources":{"soma":{"value":6,"max":6},"xp":0,"wounds":{"value":0,"max":3},"darkness":{"value":0,"max":6}},"opposition":{"defaultLevel":5,"modifier":0},"bookmark":{"wound1":"","wound2":"","wound3":"","extraWound":""}},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241652,"modifiedTime":1783973241652,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"bYXzI7NIBjuLoGE6","name":"Loki the Deceiver","type":"hunter","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/avatars/pregens/lost-stories-loki-the-deceiver.png","items":[{"_id":"wMxaiwxmCmzhyFw5","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Loki the Deceiver","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-principal.loki-the-deceiver","ownerKey":"cazador.loki-the-deceiver","role":"principal-descriptor","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"I can disguise myself to assume any identity. I can easily imitate \nmen, women, and even fantastical creatures. I have great respect \nfor a successful deception and hate to expose it, even if it would \nbenefit me.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 10.","positive":"I can disguise myself to assume any identity. I can easily imitate men, women, and even fantastical creatures. I have great respect for a successful deception and hate to expose it, even if it would benefit me.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Loki the Deceiver","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-principal.loki-the-deceiver"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241653,"modifiedTime":1783973241653,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"gigycI0DDGQ5XTZf","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Loki the Deceiver","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.loki-the-deceiver","ownerKey":"cazador.loki-the-deceiver","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1}},"system":{"description":"I am a skilled acrobat, I tell stories, perform magic tricks, and put \nmy audience in a good mood. I enjoy chaos and adding confusion \nto situations is a way for me to bring balance to the world.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 10.","positive":"I am a skilled acrobat, I tell stories, perform magic tricks, and put my audience in a good mood. I enjoy chaos and adding confusion to situations is a way for me to bring balance to the world.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Loki the Deceiver","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.loki-the-deceiver"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241653,"modifiedTime":1783973241653,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"x7KIVz4HgyHLxA1X","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Loki the Deceiver","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.loki-the-deceiver","ownerKey":"cazador.loki-the-deceiver","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2}},"system":{"description":"I am a master at distorting and unraveling deception. Verbal \nand body language hold no secrets for me. I don’t like to get my \nhands dirty and would rather have someone else do it for me.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 10.","positive":"I am a master at distorting and unraveling deception. Verbal and body language hold no secrets for me. I don’t like to get my hands dirty and would rather have someone else do it for me.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Loki the Deceiver","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.loki-the-deceiver"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241653,"modifiedTime":1783973241653,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"gJa4Ga6QDII8EBQM","name":"Thousand Faces","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Loki the Deceiver","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don1.loki-the-deceiver","ownerKey":"cazador.loki-the-deceiver","role":"gift","sequence":1}},"system":{"description":"Once per Scene, you can assume the identity of \nanother Hunter. Choose a Hunter’s Sheet that no one is using and use it \nfor the rest of the Scene. Y ou have access to all the Gifts and abilities on \nthe Sheet, with the exception of the Soma points and Wounds, which you \nwill keep from Loki’s Sheet. Even though you have their likeness, you are \nnot the Hunter you are impersonating, so you do not know their personal \nhistory and cannot activate the Special Scenario Gifts associated with \nthem. Any effects of the Gifts you activate while impersonating another \nHunter will end when you return to your true identity or at the end of \nthe Scene. If someone discovers who you really are, your masquerade \nends and you take 1 Wound. If you wish, you can return to your original \nappearance before the end of the Scene. If you discover a deception and \ndo nothing to expose it, you gain 1 Soma.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 10.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Loki the Deceiver","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","key":"don1.loki-the-deceiver"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241653,"modifiedTime":1783973241653,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"J01InEGQSikATdXy","name":"Trickster","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Loki the Deceiver","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","contentKey":"don2.loki-the-deceiver","ownerKey":"cazador.loki-the-deceiver","role":"gift","sequence":2}},"system":{"description":"Y ou get 2 Additional Successes if you use your skills as \nan entertainer to perform an action. This includes polite conversation, \nsleight of hand, or performing stunts. Once per Scene, if you help an \nenemy (for example as a Cost), you gain 1 Soma.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 10.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Loki the Deceiver","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","key":"don2.loki-the-deceiver"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241653,"modifiedTime":1783973241653,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"OCVoWul6I2aizlZm","name":"Dark Ego - The Great Deception","type":"darkEgo","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Loki the Deceiver","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","contentKey":"darkego.loki-the-deceiver","ownerKey":"cazador.loki-the-deceiver","role":"dark-ego","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"The whole world is a lie, and only \nthose who are truly aware of it can pull the strings of any story. During \nthe course of the Scene, you can activate each of the following effects \nonce:\n1. Materialize an item that is useful for the situation you are facing and \nthat an ally of yours is carrying without knowing it.\n2. Switch places with a Minor NPC. The exchange takes place in the \nblink of an eye, and those present will only see where you are now \nand where your target has ended up. Highly skilled NPCs and other \nHunters are immune to this effect.\n3. Make an NPC that you have met before appear in the Scene. This is \nan illusion that will do your bidding and will dissolve as soon as it \ntakes 1 Wound or it becomes clear that it is not the real person.\n4. Gain 1 Additional Success in a Check you make by exploiting a \nsubject’s character flaw.","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 10.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"trigger":"Organize a deception by studying it in detail, or expose a \ndeception to the people being deceived.","owner":"Loki the Deceiver","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","key":"darkego.loki-the-deceiver"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241653,"modifiedTime":1783973241653,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"m26X0FOr4LobnuXd","name":"Theatrical costume","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Loki the Deceiver","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment1.loki-the-deceiver","ownerKey":"cazador.loki-the-deceiver","role":"equipment","sequence":1}},"system":{"description":"Theatrical costume","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 10.","quantity":1,"owner":"Loki the Deceiver","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","key":"equipment1.loki-the-deceiver"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241653,"modifiedTime":1783973241653,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"5YZweCDa45HQfyqc","name":"A snake-shaped flask containing a strong acid","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Loki the Deceiver","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment2.loki-the-deceiver","ownerKey":"cazador.loki-the-deceiver","role":"equipment","sequence":2}},"system":{"description":"A snake-shaped flask containing a strong acid","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 10.","quantity":1,"owner":"Loki the Deceiver","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","key":"equipment2.loki-the-deceiver"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241653,"modifiedTime":1783973241653,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"QMyOiuCRK6kqNNVV","name":"A necklace of great value engraved with the word “Brísingamen”","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Loki the Deceiver","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment3.loki-the-deceiver","ownerKey":"cazador.loki-the-deceiver","role":"equipment","sequence":3}},"system":{"description":"A necklace of great value engraved with the word “Brísingamen”","notes":"See bt-ls-hunters-sheets-1.2-eng-BASE-SCREEN.pdf, pages 10.","quantity":1,"owner":"Loki the Deceiver","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","key":"equipment3.loki-the-deceiver"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241653,"modifiedTime":1783973241653,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"nbqq8Tuugx4VF3ri","name":"Various musical instruments and juggling equipment","type":"equipment","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Loki the Deceiver","source":"Lost Stories","category":"hunter","contentKey":"equipment4.loki-the-deceiver","ownerKey":"caza